(361, 72, 'interview_content', 'I first started following the work of David Gensler around 7 years ago and have continued to watch his advancements in the creative industry. He founded The Keystone Design Union (KDU) in 2003 with the goal to bring together the most accomplished, creative professionals and currently represents more than 1,500 of them internationally. Serum Versus Venom was also launched in 2003 and is one of New York’s most underrated, non-branded, and most authentic clothing lines. I recently had the opportunity to interview David and ask questions about his life, business, luxuries and whats coming up next.'),
